-- Krones Expects Record Sales in 2011, CFO Tells Euro am Sonntag
-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 2011-12-18T11:45:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-18/krones-expects-record-sales-in-2011-cfo-tells-euro-am-sonntag.html
Krones AG , a German maker of
machines for the bottling and packaging industry, expects to
report record sales this year, Chief Financial Officer Hans- Juergen Thaus told  Euro am Sonntag .  Revenue this year will exceed the 2.38 billion euros ($3.1
billion) record in 2008, Thaus told the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Nicola in Berlin at 
